<div class="container mt-4 mb-4">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <p class="text-box h4 overflow-hidden">
                With fluctuations in the costs of living,
                families and individuals are increasingly harder to afford basic living needs
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <p class="text-box h4 overflow-hidden">Foodbanks across the country have risen to the challenge of helping the public through these difficult times</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <p class="text-box h4 overflow-hidden">Here you can find and up-to-date database of foodbanks and their distribution centers accross the UK</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container mt-4 col-10">
    <div class="row bg-success" style="background-color: #115649;">
        <div class="col-9 d-grid mx-auto">
            <p class="h4 text-center text-light">Apply to register your foodbank into our database and make it easier for people to find you</p>
            <div class="mt-3 mb-3 d-grid col-5 mx-auto">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" asp-area="" asp-page="/Foodbank/AddBank">Register Foodbank</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
