<div class="container mt-5">

    <div class="row ">
        <div class="col-sm-3">
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h1 class="text-center">Foodbanks</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-2">
            <img src="/img/TT-Logo.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="Trussell Trust Logo"/>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <p class="text-box">
                Most foodbanks are branch locations of the Trussell Trust. These foodbanks require users to obtain a referral and vougher from an issuing authority. Details of these agencies can be obtained from the Citezens Advice Bureau.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-2">
            <img src="/img/TT-Voucher.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="IFAN logo"/>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <p class="text-box">
                Foodbank vouches are required to obtain food from most foodbanks. These are issued by several organisations suchj a Local council, Housing Options, Social services, some community clinics, other NHS services, some charitable organisations.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-2">
            <img src="/img/IFAN-Logo.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="IFAN logo"/>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <p class="text-box ">
                Independent Food Aid Network is an organisation that lists many independent foodbanks. A referral is not always required to obtain food from these foodbanks. Check with your local IFAN foodbank before setting out

            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-2">
            <img src="/img/Independent-logo.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="Independent foodbanks"/>
        </div>
        <div class=" col-sm-4">
            <p class="text-box">
                Independent foodbanks may be affiliated to another organisation such as The Salvation Army or the NHS for example, or are small independets that have no affiliation. These foodbanks may or may not have a particular access requirements. Always check before setting out

            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>